TriviaSpoilers

–block


- This takes place in the same universe as michael the kiler.

- N/A and Toughy are SCP-5045-2 and D-6770 respectively, if that wasn't obvious.

- Farmer usually puts on a fake Texas accent, but sometimes he just drops it completely, usually when frustrated.

- Farmer is satisfied with what he's done to Site-301. Yep, it's a complete farm facility now!

- Every normal human in the SCP-5045 world is colored in bright yellow. Those people in that purple building were not just copies of SCP-5045-2.

- The files not having any commas is cause the font I was using didn't have any commas.

- This is an extra-dimensional anomaly. When you play this  is only an enticing label.

- Farmer is a huge manipulator.

- Farmer is using this article to getcha.

- Row, row, row your boat, gently down the stream.

- Merrily merrily, merrily, merrily, life is but a dream.




